nt teaching techniques are best suited for\ndifferent outcomes, which implies that a mix of techniques may be optimal in\ncourse design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 17:50:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 20:16:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-14"}
