face brightness distribution of Horiuchi and\ncollaborators using several combinations of these models, but we cannot\nreproduce the measured distribution of Di Mauro with any combination of models.\nOur fits provide constraints on potential pathways to explain the gamma-ray\nexcess using MSPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 21:28:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-10"}
