ic and demographic characteristics. We illustrate how real-time AQ\nreporting could be improved (or, in some cases, worsened) by using LCS, both\nfor the population overall and for marginalized communities specifically. This\nwork has implications for the integration of LCS into real-time AQ reporting\nplatforms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 23:09:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2023 22:29:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-06"}
