erical simulation results\ndemonstrate that, the proposed two stage scheme is able to outperform the\nexisting methods in both the theoretical channel model and the QuaDRiGa channel\nemulation platform.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 May 2022 09:44:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Apr 2023 10:36:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
