n, and training sample size determination, and summarize those\nprocedures as algorithms such that users can easily implement them with\ndifferent computing languages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 May 2022 10:08:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-10"}
