y a few layers, challenging the belief\nthat image recognition requires deep sequential analysis of visual objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 May 2022 11:19:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 May 2022 14:40:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 12:01:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 31 May 2023 05:30:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
